COMMITTEE AMENDMENT

COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 843, L.D. 1268
1 SUMMARY
22 This amendment, which replaces the bill and is the minority report of the committee,
33 requires the Department of Transportation to provide an annual reliability performance
44 stipend of $3,000 to all qualifying full-time state employees of the Maine State Ferry
55 Service. A qualifying employee must receive the stipend as a lump sum by December 1st
66 of each year.
